      <title>委内瑞拉大选或将延长债券市场流亡期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-bonds-slide-as-opposition-questions-maduro-s-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉总统大选引发的政治动荡有可能延长该国的经济孤立状态，并破坏任何债务重组举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/venezuela-bonds-slide-as-opposition-questions-maduro-s-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:12:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
